710799f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 56th Street
710799f-a.text:
Twelfth Ave., east side, at West 56th Street, showing under construction
the new incinerator building of the Dept. of Sanitation, on the S.E. corner
of West 56th Street.
May 21, 1936.
L Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

710800f-a.title: Manhattan: 12th Avenue - 56th Street
710800f-a.text:
Twelfth Ave., east side, north from West 56th Street. Note on the
left the elevated West Side Vehicular Express Highway.
November 23, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
